            "TableId": "/Game/UI/JournalData/Entries/ST_JournalEntries.ST_JournalEntries",
            "Key": "SkeletalHoplite",
            "SourceString": "In life the hoplites named themselves in honour of the legendary forces of Saradomin, back on Hallow. They took their identity from the sacred texts, creating a disciplined and loyal legion of skilled warriors.\r\n\r\nNow, that discipline has all but faded. They forget the shield walls, or the turtle formation. They forget the bonds they once shared with their friends. Now they only remember that a spear must be thrust forward, preferably into someone else.",
